 of Allah, it will be multiplied up to seven hundred times in his record.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1625 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u062e\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0627\u062a\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15550,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/05\/allah-multiplies-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34484,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Allah multiplies reward for spending charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone gives charity from what is good, for Allah only accepts what is good, except that the Merciful takes it with His right hand. Even if it is a date, it is nurtured in the hand\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40282,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/30\/shade-of-their-sadaqa\/","url_meta":{"origin":34484,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: All people in shade of their charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEveryone will be in the shade of their charity until judgment is c